Package: libdphys-macaddress-perl
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${perl:Depends}
Description: represent a MAC address
 A Perl Moo class to represent a MAC address.  Allows only valid
 MAC addresses (specified in one of a number of formats) and can
 convert them to some supported formats.
